text: "Tequilla Sunrise" is a 1973 song by Eagles and is the leading single from their second studio album Desperado. It went to number 64 in the United States and number 68 in Canada and was covered in 1993 by country artist Alan Jackson for the tribute album Common Thread: The Songs of the Eagles. ==References== Category:1973 songs Category:Soft rock songs Category:Country rock songs Category:Eagles (band) songs Category:Alan Jackson songs
